{"type": "article", "id": 26663, "title": "香樟木收纳盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-11T06:44:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702105801aCvWhl9jGpkNKdxM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这款开放式的香樟木收纳盒名为“多点”，由来自杭州的尤皿家居设计有限公司设计。开放式的设计让樟木芬充分散发，提升了去除异味和防霉的效果。打破条条框框的十字点则使得收纳更为随意灵活，设计时还留有细小的缝隙让木板能够在梅雨季节收缩。它目前还处于<a href=\"http://z.jd.com/project/details/50716.html\">众筹阶段</a>，最低售价为 135 元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105759ot7LnJ651qMs0zEQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105759mr7c8JPSUuO5pExy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105800TicuKBmU12HPXdGz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105800reSEmV0HOg5YBpjF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}